<text top="592" left="475" width="33" height="7" font="font8" id="p1_t85" reading_order_no="82" segment_no="13" tag_type="table">Right side<b>left radial nerve along the spiral groove with additional distal motor axonal loss due to wallerian degeneration.</b></text>
